      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, powered by the S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example is mechanically impeccable, with a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing service. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, utilizing the original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. Presented in showroom condition with a pristine interior and flawless paint, this is a turnkey collector\u2019s piece for the discerning purist.",
